channel.title: RuneUnlimited
channel.description:
I've decided, it's time to release RuneUnlimited.
This is only the source, the client was worked mostly by me and I don't wanna release something I worked very hard on.
Features: -Project Insanity base. -Almost all dupes fixed. -Almost all bugs and glitches fixed. -Flawless combat system. -Shitty Project Insanity skills, with some ideas for hunter included I believe. -Home is in Fally.
Anti-Leech Yeah, have fun. There are about 5 "}" missing from Client.java, good luck putting them back in. The CFG files have been tampered with, and server.java has a important line missing..
Want more information? http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,469278.msg3430867.html#msg3430867
Don't bitch about pictures, because I'm not posting any, other than the virus scan. [IMG]http://i661.photobucket.com/albums/uu331/deathlyags/Capture_221.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i661.photobucket.com/albums/uu331/deathlyags/Capture_220.jpg[/img]
Additional information. This server is very stable, I loaded 2,500 onto the server and got no lag. The speed was slow, but thats because I only have 4 GB ram >_>... Anyways, I'm releasing because I feel I wont have enough time to work on this due to school and a recent surprised death in the family. I wish all the best for those who decide to work on this, and good luck.
Credits. -John (Me) - Fixing what Sanity fucked up. -Sanity -Graham -AMG A Bear -Mystic Flow If you think I missed you, PM me and I will fix.
